– Hi! I present to you my map “fun_testroid_boxik” for "Counter-Strike: Source" – a „fun” type of map, very small, with ultrashort and hot battles.
Here are some physical destroyable objects (a wall and three types of pillars), made by myself.

At the beginning it was a very simple map for testing.
But a good friend saw the map and tried it. After this he said that he want "to live" on it and to call everyone to be guest here.
Well, yeah, I edit it and will give them this pleasure. -))
I am game developer, but in such way I accumulate experience in level-design and keep fit.

Notes: Fun map (atypical maps that can combine several types of gameplay, but often it is funny or just wacky maps, made for fun).
------------------------------------
Background story of the map:
An extremely important mission for survival and domination!
- Special Forces and terrorists at the same time came to the public WC. Oops, surprise!
However, everyone wants to make a shit.
But someone is sitting on the toilet, making everyone to wait outside.
Oh shit!
Now have to figure out who first will remain to make a shit in comfort.
------------------------------------
Maximal number of players on this map: 32 (real players, or 31 bots & 1 real player).
But is desirable no more than 8 players (real players, or 7 bots & 1 real player).
Recommended 6 players (real players, or 5 bots & 1 real player).

Success and have a good hunting! :)

This map was created to find a balance between aim and power.

Terrorists: After the warm-up timer you will be teleported into the middle of the arena with an AWP, in plain sight of the ct's. You need to keep them from reaching you while dodging headshots. The only things that can kill you are: a headshot, two ct's hitting you at once, falling into the lava, being stabbed in the back, or being shot by the cannon. Basically, they have to do 100+ damage in a half of a second, or you don't die.

Counter-Terrorists: You are on the edges of the arena with scouts. You will need to use teamwork to call shots or coordinate the terrorists' deaths. You are concealed and hard to see, so use your terrain wisely.

Traps: While inside the arena two traps will commence. One trap sends boulders hurling at you from the sky, another drops half of the terrorists' floor into lava. These can be used to both teams' advantages. For the terrorists, the boulders can block the counter-terrorists' bullets and the floor can keep them from getting close to you and stabbing you in the back, resulting in an instant kill. For the counter-terrorists, you will love seeing terrorists being crushed by boulders and being incinerated in the lava pool.

I hope you enjoy this map.

This is my second map. I hope you guys like it.
It is a map with close battles. The T's can either choose to camp behind a corner or run for a better weapon. The counter-terrorist can choose to stay high and keep the T low, or enter the secret tunnel in ct spawn. If a player wants a good weapon he has to take a big risk, because you have to go to spots where you can get easily killed. Also, T's can get a scout, however, they are likely to get killed by nades if they get there.
I really tried a lot of different ways to keep the t vs ct fair and let them take risks for better weapons or hide with a weaker one.

This map was based off a part of my previous map.
The objective of this map is to destroy all of the fruit before the other teams does.
You will need to work together to beat the other team.

There are 10 spawns for each team
Which makes a total of 20 slots for this map.

The map consists of 3 stages with different fruit on each stage.
There is also a coffee cup that was placed on each level for difficulty.
The glass will break after all the fruit is destroyed on that level.

NOTE: For the banana bunches, you do not have to destroy all of the little bananas, just the bunches.

Questions or concerns? Please ask away.
Thankyou, Trexxasaurus.

Zak - mentioning the idea
Major Pain - design of map
Chelsea's Server - testing the map

I always wanted a hard, but fun map to play with a twist. So what i made was, bombs, dropping from the sky. >:)

Obsticle Course:
Dodge bombs
Run to cover
Dodge bombs
Run up hill
Swim and dodge bombs
Run up ramp, into water, safe zone is in water
Dodge bombs
Run to other water stack
Run to building, climb up
Jump down onto a water pile
Press the slay button (slays other team for the win)

The big building is climbable on the side facing you. Press the slay button after jumping down to slay other team. What ever team presses button first wins (cause other team will all die). If the button dosnt kill them all, keep pressing it >:).*NO FIGHTING ON THIS MAP*

WATCH OUT FOR THE BOMBS!!!

Have Fun!!! :)

***WARNING***: This map can cause CSS to crash on slower or weak machines.
